rerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/leaf/6a54571c62478.jpg" width="2055"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://leaf.some.pics"&gt;@leaf&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 03:10:23 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5456ca580de</link><description>&lt;p&gt;咖啡群岛 2/3&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A piece of paper with some coffee splotches on it. The coffee splotches have been traced around with a pen. It begins to look slightly like islands drawn on a map." height="2260" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/leaf/6a5456ca580de.jpg" width="1702"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://leaf.some.pics"&gt;@leaf&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 03:09:01 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>